protecting the second rank and preparing to double rooks on the c-file.} Rg6
23. Qe2 a6 24. Rec1 h5 {and now White came up with an interesting decision -}
25. Bxe4 $5 Qxe4 26. Qf3 Qe5 27. Rc5 Rd8 28. Qf4 $5 {and after} Qxf4 29. exf4
