-Jorquera Cahuin,M (2327) Internet Section 09A g/8'+2" blitz 2004 (8) 1/2-1/2}
11. Bc4 Qe4 12. Bxf7+ $1) 11. e4 e5 $8 12. b5 $5 {White creates a dangerous
