Yd4b5]} a6 11. Rd1 Qb6 $2 12. Ndb5 $1 axb5 13. Nd5 $18) 8. Ndb5 $1 {[%cal
Gc3d5] Black is already in a difficult situation.} Qb6 (8... Na6 9. Rc1 Be7 10.
