[%cal Re4d5]} Nce7 22. d5 Qa4 23. Bxc7 $16 {[%csl Gd5]}) 18. Qc4+ $1 {The most
precise move. The idea is to take the d4-knight with a pawn.} Kh8 19. cxd4 $16
